title: Ezekiel Elliot, Eli Manning, Josh Rosen and the NFL Preseason
itunes:title: Ezekiel Elliot, Eli Manning, Josh Rosen and the NFL Preseason
description:
Colin comments on the possibility of the Cowboys playing without Ezekiel Elliott, what the Giants are probably doing with Eli Manning, Josh Rosen not starting for the Dolphins, and what the preseason has shown us. Guests include Eric Dickerson, Andy Reid, Jason Whitlock, Steve Beuerlein and Jason McIntyre.
